1
00:00:01,880 --> 00:00:04,480
What? There was another surrender 
without any bloodshed?

2
00:00:04,750 --> 00:00:07,730
Honestly... How can they be so disloyal?

3
00:00:08,030 --> 00:00:10,530
Well, the viceroys in remote regions

4
00:00:10,530 --> 00:00:16,080
were those who were demoted for 
opposing the capital in the first place.

5
00:00:16,080 --> 00:00:18,100
It's no surprise they would betray us.

6
00:00:18,100 --> 00:00:21,590
H-However, if this keeps up, 
the rebel army will reach the capitalâ€”

7
00:00:21,590 --> 00:00:22,830
Stop panicking.

8
00:00:23,360 --> 00:00:25,520
C-Commander-in-Chief Budou...

9
00:00:25,520 --> 00:00:28,800
They say the military should keep 
their mouth shut about politics.

10
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:33,330
I've abided by that maxim, 
but given the circumstances,

11
00:00:33,330 --> 00:00:36,060
I can't keep quiet, either, Minister.

12
00:00:36,060 --> 00:00:39,330
My, that's harsh...

13
00:00:39,330 --> 00:00:41,160
"Protect this kingdom."

14
00:00:41,160 --> 00:00:45,730
For a thousand years, this mission has 
been bestowed upon my family.

15
00:00:45,730 --> 00:00:50,850
I shall sever whatever disturbs the 
nation's peace, with my own hands.

16
00:00:50,850 --> 00:00:52,930
Regardless of who or what it may be.

17
00:00:52,930 --> 00:00:55,030
Oh, how terrifying.

18
00:00:55,030 --> 00:00:57,330
But you need not worry.

19
00:00:57,330 --> 00:01:02,030
Even if the masses rebel, 
we have countermeasures in place.

20
00:01:02,790 --> 00:01:04,910
Allow me to introduce you...

21
00:01:04,910 --> 00:01:07,800
In order to maintain public 
order within the capital,

22
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:10,980
a new elite unit has been established!

23
00:01:11,690 --> 00:01:13,300
Pardon the intrusion.

24
00:01:16,810 --> 00:01:18,750
He's too incompetent to be a commander,

25
00:01:18,750 --> 00:01:22,730
but I've chosen my son, Shura, for the job.

26
00:01:23,880 --> 00:01:26,480
Ah, so you're the infamous Commander-in-Chief.

27
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:29,730
I heard that only General Esdeath 
can match your strength.

28
00:01:31,150 --> 00:01:33,810
There's no need for someone 
of your rank to step in,

29
00:01:33,810 --> 00:01:35,660
just because some have decided to rebel.

30
00:01:35,660 --> 00:01:37,430
Simply leave it to me.

31
00:01:37,810 --> 00:01:39,490
Oh? Where are you going?

32
00:01:40,050 --> 00:01:44,050
There are always a few rats that sniff around

33
00:01:44,050 --> 00:01:46,830
before the whole swarm arrives.

34
00:01:47,080 --> 00:01:50,960
Jeez... Doesn't he know he 
can sit back and relax?

35
00:01:51,300 --> 00:01:52,780
Now, Shura...

36
00:01:52,780 --> 00:01:55,800
I'll be observing what you can do.

37
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:59,550
To determine whether you're 
worthy to be my successor.

38
00:01:59,850 --> 00:02:02,340
Yeah, I'll be looking forward to it.

39
00:02:02,930 --> 00:02:04,830
<i>Hunting some rats, huh?</i>

40
00:02:04,830 --> 00:02:07,220
<i>It'll be the perfect warm-up.</i>

41
00:03:39,460 --> 00:03:41,200
Kill the Carnage

42
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:42,950
Kill the Carnage

43
