Kurome, is your body really okay?

45
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:55,910
There are no issues.

46
00:03:58,980 --> 00:04:00,180
Here you are.

47
00:04:00,180 --> 00:04:03,050
I don't know if it's as good 
as what Bols used to make.

48
00:04:04,900 --> 00:04:06,260
Have you heard, Wave?

49
00:04:06,700 --> 00:04:10,370
Supposedly, the minister has created 
an elite unit he directly supervises.

50
00:04:10,370 --> 00:04:11,570
Seems that way.

51
00:04:11,570 --> 00:04:13,660
Captain Esdeath is away on an expedition.

52
00:04:14,100 --> 00:04:17,980
And the Jaegers are down to 
half of what we started with.

53
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:23,150
But isn't that exactly why we should 
be the ones on the front lines?

54
00:04:23,150 --> 00:04:25,020
Why would they put us on standby?

55
00:04:25,410 --> 00:04:28,830
This must mean the capital has 
more than one central figure.

56
00:04:28,830 --> 00:04:31,080
What the hell are they thinking?!

57
00:04:31,310 --> 00:04:35,960
At times like these, we should unite to 
stop the rebel army in their tracks!

58
00:04:37,050 --> 00:04:37,630
Seconds.

59
00:04:37,630 --> 00:04:38,710
So fast!

60
00:04:39,110 --> 00:04:42,300
Man, as always, you're a bottomless pit.

61
