71
00:05:00,230 --> 00:05:03,740
Yeah, the capital's gonna be 
a battle zone soon, too.

72
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,860
We'll take advantage of that commotion,

73
00:05:05,860 --> 00:05:07,480
sneak into the palace,

74
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:09,200
and kill the minister.

75
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:11,490
You've steeled your resolve, right, Tatsumi?

76
00:05:11,490 --> 00:05:12,980
Of course I have.

77
00:05:13,490 --> 00:05:17,250
But I want as few civilian casualties as possible.

78
00:05:17,850 --> 00:05:21,290
So the sooner we defeat the minister, the better.

79
00:05:21,830 --> 00:05:23,200
Well said.

80
00:05:23,200 --> 00:05:24,200
Now, then...

81
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:26,880
It's almost time to meet the resistance.

82
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:28,180
Let's go.

83
00:05:30,500 --> 00:05:33,730
I'm surprised they made such a 
complicated underground channel.

84
00:05:33,730 --> 00:05:37,040
As the capital flourished, it probably 
became bigger and bigger.

85
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:37,850
Pointlessly.

86
00:05:38,190 --> 00:05:41,730
And it was managed so poorly, 
there aren't any accurate maps.

87
00:05:42,060 --> 00:05:44,990
