you two are pretty cozy!

94
00:06:02,340 --> 00:06:04,170
D-Don't be stupid.

95
00:06:04,170 --> 00:06:07,150
Nothing's changed! In fact, 
it isn't like that at all!

96
00:06:07,150 --> 00:06:08,300
What, you want to die?

97
00:06:08,300 --> 00:06:09,750
Stop getting so worked up.

98
00:06:09,750 --> 00:06:11,080
