I might snatch him for myself...

101
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:19,530
You can't do that!

102
00:06:23,380 --> 00:06:25,370
You're finally being honest.

103
00:06:25,370 --> 00:06:28,240
Well, regardless, I'll be taking him.

104
00:06:31,530 --> 00:06:33,830
Stop saying stupid things. 
We're here to work.

105
00:06:33,830 --> 00:06:35,080
Work!

106
00:06:35,080 --> 00:06:36,260
All right, all right.

107
00:06:37,740 --> 00:06:38,870
