112
00:06:48,540 --> 00:06:50,810
No, this was to be expected.

113
00:06:51,310 --> 00:06:53,300
We'll carry out our mission as planned.

114
00:06:53,670 --> 00:06:57,430
When we infiltrate the palace, 
you kill the guards.

115
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:58,660
I'm counting on you.

116
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,020
Understood.

117
00:07:00,910 --> 00:07:04,110
<i>I'm also relying on you, Tatsumi and Lubbock.</i>

118
00:07:05,290 --> 00:07:06,510
Hey, Tatsumi?

119
00:07:06,510 --> 00:07:07,260
Hm?

120
00:07:07,260 --> 00:07:10,030
After this battle, what will you do?

121
00:07:11,170 --> 00:07:15,220
Uh, I've never really given it any thought...

122
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:16,830
What about you?

123
00:07:16,830 --> 00:07:19,500
I'm gonna continue running the bookstore.

124
00:07:19,500 --> 00:07:23,350
I'll expand the store, and eventually, 
I'll turn it into a national franchise.

125
00:07:23,700 --> 00:07:24,590
Wow.

126
00:07:24,590 --> 00:07:28,340
Then I'll wait for the right time 
to propose to Miss Najenda!

127
00:07:28,690 --> 00:07:31,570
Oh, yeah? That's great.

128
00:07:31,570 --> 00:07:33,320
And how's it going with you?

129
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:34,600
And Mine?

130
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:36,580
Mine has nothing to do with me.

131
00:07:36,580 --> 00:07:38,320
Don't play dumb.

132
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:40,230
Ever since we got back from Kyoroch,

133
00:07:40,230 --> 00:07:42,760
