147
00:08:25,660 --> 00:08:27,650
and both my mother and he were incarcerated.

148
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:29,160
I see.

149
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:33,030
Then, does that mean other Revolutionary 
Army members are also within the palace?

150
00:08:33,550 --> 00:08:34,560
Yes.

151
00:08:34,560 --> 00:08:37,270
The bureaucracy that opposes the minister

152
00:08:37,270 --> 00:08:40,370
has been in covert communications 
with the Revolutionary Army.

153
00:08:40,930 --> 00:08:44,120
So our role is to work with these people

154
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:48,290
and support the Revolutionary 
Army's break-in from within.

155
00:08:48,630 --> 00:08:50,920
Oh, that's reassuring.

156
00:08:51,290 --> 00:08:54,370
That's why you, who can turn invisible,

157
00:08:54,370 --> 00:08:57,230
and I, the espionage expert, 
were chosen for this mission.

158
00:08:57,230 --> 00:08:58,390
We have to pull this off.

159
00:08:58,390 --> 00:08:59,340
Right.

160
00:09:05,470 --> 00:09:06,400
This is it.

161
00:09:15,390 --> 00:09:16,250
What is it?

162
00:09:16,710 --> 00:09:17,810
Something's wrong.

163
00:09:18,250 --> 00:09:22,300
Normally, someone knocks from 
the inside to confirm...

164
00:09:23,880 --> 00:09:24,580
Get back.

165
00:09:33,990 --> 00:09:35,670
Th-This is...

166
00:09:35,670 --> 00:09:37,910
